::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Unparalleled... One takes the head across an army ten-thousand strong!
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504121011-->
:::'''"Dux Carminum" Verginia:''' Clean and swift, yet without forsaking grandeur...
::<pre>{
