::'''"Dux Carminum" Verginia:''' Listen now to the Gladius's final tremor... (Unparalleled... One takes the head across an army ten-thousand strong!/This blade... shall sever the Titan's head!/The golden blood is like dew, and the sea runs as clear as a river.)
