:::'''"Dux Carminum" Verginia:''' Th&mdash;Thank you! I'm not used to opening a conversation, so p&mdash;please go easy on me!
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Let's talk about your past.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504121106-->
::::'''"Dux Carminum" Verginia:''' Where to begin... If I start from the very beginning, I remember being born into an unknown tribe in the outskirts of Castrum Kremnos...
::::'''"Dux Carminum" Verginia:''' Ah, s&mdash;sorry, you probably don't want to hear such trivial things. Let me start from when I was expelled from Castrum Kremnos.
::::'''"Dux Carminum" Verginia:''' Since I was young, I was very frail and weak. I couldn't even l&mdash;lift the lightest spear.
::::'''"Dux Carminum" Verginia:''' But I loved everything r&mdash;romantic! I loved beautiful headscarves, loved burrowing in the library reading stories, and most of all, I l&mdash;loved reciting poetry!
::::'''"Dux Carminum" Verginia:''' After leaving Castrum Kremnos, I spent some time as a bard. By chance, the Great Imperator saw my heroic ode and brought me into the army to serve as a chronicler for the Flame-Chase Army.
::::'''"Dux Carminum" Verginia:''' Once I finish ''Heroic Saga of Flame-Chase'', I'll be able to repay the Great Imperator's kindness in taking me in.
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Let's talk about your future.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504121113-->
::::'''"Dux Carminum" Verginia:''' My future... I haven't given it much thought. Or rather, I d&mdash;dared not to hope for the future I desire.
::::'''"Dux Carminum" Verginia:''' After all, after Ocean, there are still Trickery, Death, Sky, Strife... With so many mighty Titans to overcome, a weak Chrysos Heir like me... m&mdash;might just end up throwing my life away in battle.
::::'''"Dux Carminum" Verginia:''' As for the future the Great Imperator promised...
::::'''"Dux Carminum" Verginia:''' Reciting poetry on a stage like the universe is intriguing, b&mdash;but it's also terrifying!
::::'''"Dux Carminum" Verginia:''' However, if it comes to that, my comrades a&mdash;and Apollonius will probably cheer me on from behind!
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Exit}} Done chatting for now.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504121119-->
::::'''"Dux Carminum" Verginia:''' O&mdash;Okay, have fun at the feast, (Trailblazer)...
::::<!--Custom String Trigger: ALL_TALK_END-->
::::<!--Custom String Listener: ALL_TALK_END-->
