:::'''"Dux Carminum" Verginia:''' Huh? I&mdash;I don't have any secrets I'm hiding, only an open one&mdash;
:::'''"Dux Carminum" Verginia:''' I l&mdash;like Apollonius, I want to accompany him in this endless feast, forever, and ever...
